Obtain Reference Signatures

Source: R/get_sig_similarity.R
get_sig_db.Rd

The signatures and their aetiologies mainly obtained from COSMIC database and cleaned before saving into sigminer package.

get_sig_db(sig_db = "legacy")

Arguments

sig_db

can be 'legacy' (for COSMIC v2 'SBS'), 'SBS', 'DBS', 'ID' and 'TSB' (for SBS transcriptional strand bias signatures). Default 'legacy'.

Value

a list.

See also

get_sig_similarity, sig_fit and show_cosmic_sig_profile.

Examples

s1 <- get_sig_db()
s2 <- get_sig_db("DBS")
s1
